WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:04.680
Good morning, everybody. I wanted to come

00:00:02.700 --> 00:00:07.500
on today and just tell everybody a quick

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:09.300
testimony of what God did for us a

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.980
couple of years ago now.

00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:12.780
We

00:00:09.980 --> 00:00:15.719
were cleaning the rugs at the

00:00:12.780 --> 00:00:17.880
church on Saturday, and we

00:00:15.719 --> 00:00:21.480
were driving home; we were headed home.

00:00:17.880 --> 00:00:23.640
The gas gauge on the

00:00:21.480 --> 00:00:26.580
truck that we had was completely

00:00:23.640 --> 00:00:29.460
broken, and I didn't realize how low

00:00:26.580 --> 00:00:31.919
we were on gas. We were

00:00:29.460 --> 00:00:35.100
driving down the highway when, all of a

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:37.440
sudden, the truck just went dead

00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:40.739
and ran out of gas. It was probably

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:42.360
about 105 degrees in July; it was

00:00:40.739 --> 00:00:46.140
really hot outside. My wife was pregnant

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:48.420
with our daughter at the time, and

00:00:46.140 --> 00:00:50.340
my son and my other daughter were in the

00:00:48.420 --> 00:00:51.960
back seat. As

00:00:50.340 --> 00:00:55.440
I pulled

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:57.840
over, my wife asked, "What's wrong?"and I said,

00:00:55.440 --> 00:01:00.599
"I think we

00:00:57.840 --> 00:01:02.340
just ran out of gas."We started

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:05.519
getting really nervous because it was so

00:01:02.340 --> 00:01:08.100
hot outside. I

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:09.780
rolled down the windows and

00:01:08.100 --> 00:01:12.600
started praying in the Holy Spirit,

00:01:09.780 --> 00:01:13.799
asking God for mercy

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:16.439
because I didn't want to get out of the

00:01:13.799 --> 00:01:18.960
truck and walk down the highway with a

00:01:16.439 --> 00:01:22.919
pregnant wife and two kids.

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:26.639
My son was six and my daughter was

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:29.700
10. So I was

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:31.860
just praying and, all of a sudden,

00:01:29.700 --> 00:01:35.520
out of nowhere, I'm holding the steering

00:01:31.860 --> 00:01:38.340
wheel and I feel this bang on the back

00:01:35.520 --> 00:01:41.100
of our truck and it jolted us forward.

00:01:38.340 --> 00:01:44.280
I thought we were rear-ended; that's

00:01:41.100 --> 00:01:47.759
how hard it was. I looked in my rearview mirror—and

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:51.360
I'm

00:01:47.759 --> 00:01:53.939
seeing in the spirit at this time—and I

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:56.220
see an angel smiling at me

00:01:53.939 --> 00:01:58.199
in the spirit realm, grinning from ear to

00:01:56.220 --> 00:02:00.240
ear. He was this big, heavy-set guy,

00:01:58.200 --> 00:02:06.060
kind of like I am; he was chunky-looking. He had

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:08.880
huge, massive wings

00:02:06.060 --> 00:02:11.879
spanned out on the back, and he had

00:02:08.880 --> 00:02:17.220
a hold of my tailgate. All of a

00:02:11.879 --> 00:02:17.220
sudden, we started moving supernaturally

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:22.500
down the road; he started pushing us faster and

00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:25.260
faster. I was shook up at this

00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:27.000
time; I was

00:02:25.260 --> 00:02:29.099
in shock. We started

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:30.720
moving, and as I held onto

00:02:29.099 --> 00:02:32.700
the steering wheel, I turned

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:34.739
my

00:02:32.700 --> 00:02:37.379
blinker on to get back on the highway.

00:02:34.739 --> 00:02:40.379
My wife's like, "My God, what's going on?"We

00:02:37.379 --> 00:02:43.018
were all just freaking out. We

00:02:40.379 --> 00:02:46.799
were going faster and faster, and

00:02:43.019 --> 00:02:49.019
I'm in the left-hand lane. We were gathering

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:51.360
so

00:02:49.019 --> 00:02:54.019
much speed that we started passing people in

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:59.040
the right-hand lane all the way down.

00:02:54.019 --> 00:03:02.480
That angel pushes us three miles to the

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:07.319
next gas station. We exit the highway.

00:03:02.480 --> 00:03:11.159
We stop at the stoplight.

00:03:07.319 --> 00:03:13.859
He pushes us through the stoplight down

00:03:11.159 --> 00:03:17.159
the street another block or so.

00:03:13.860 --> 00:03:20.099
We turn right and then we go right into

00:03:17.159 --> 00:03:23.280
the gas station, and he yanks the

00:03:20.099 --> 00:03:24.480
tailgate of that truck, and we stop in

00:03:23.280 --> 00:03:27.780
front of the pump.

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:30.119
When he did, we all just started

00:03:27.780 --> 00:03:32.519
screaming and praising God at the pump.

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:34.739
People at the other pumps were

00:03:32.519 --> 00:03:36.659
looking at us like, "What is wrong with them?"you

00:03:34.739 --> 00:03:39.300
know, but we were just so

00:03:36.659 --> 00:03:41.519
excited that we just had an angelic

00:03:39.300 --> 00:03:44.099
visitation.

00:03:41.519 --> 00:03:46.260
My kids didn't see it, nor did my wife, but

00:03:44.099 --> 00:03:47.819
we all felt the truck moving. We

00:03:46.260 --> 00:03:50.819
were going so fast down

00:03:47.819 --> 00:03:52.679
the highway; everybody knew it.

00:03:50.819 --> 00:03:54.958
When we got to the pump

00:03:52.680 --> 00:03:57.299
at the gas station, we all just started

00:03:54.959 --> 00:03:58.799
worshiping. It was just a

00:03:57.299 --> 00:04:01.140
really cool moment. Everybody was just

00:03:58.799 --> 00:04:03.180
like, "Wow,"and we all just started laughing. We

00:04:01.140 --> 00:04:06.720
just got so full of joy at

00:04:03.180 --> 00:04:09.360
what God just did. So

00:04:06.720 --> 00:04:12.299
I just wanted to come on and tell

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:15.239
everybody this testimony about what

00:04:12.299 --> 00:04:17.519
happened for my children

00:04:15.239 --> 00:04:19.680
and me, that the Lord took care of us.

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:22.380
We didn't have to have my

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:24.419
wife go through it by herself in the

00:04:22.380 --> 00:04:26.100
middle of the heat and do all that. It

00:04:24.419 --> 00:04:28.198
was a dangerous situation and he came

00:04:26.100 --> 00:04:31.080
through for us. So I just wanted to tell

00:04:28.199 --> 00:04:34.340
everybody about the goodness of God

00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:38.159
and what He does. If you believe,

00:04:34.340 --> 00:04:40.799
all things are possible to him that

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:44.160
believes. And nothing's too big

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:46.440
for God. I have testimony after

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:48.419
testimony that I'm going to

00:04:46.440 --> 00:04:51.000
document. I'm going to put them on here so people

00:04:48.419 --> 00:04:53.539
can hear about the goodness of God and

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:58.199
what He's still doing today. Jesus Christ is

00:04:53.540 --> 00:05:00.419
the same yesterday, today, and forever. And

00:04:58.199 --> 00:05:03.840
the miracles that He did two thousand

00:05:00.419 --> 00:05:06.240
years ago, He will still do today if you

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:09.119
believe Him for them. I believe with all

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:10.979
my heart. I've seen it time and time

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:14.280
again, and I'm going to tell you about

00:05:10.979 --> 00:05:17.340
each one of them. Stay tuned. Thank you

00:05:14.280 --> 00:05:20.119
for watching, and if you could give us

00:05:17.340 --> 00:05:23.099
a thumbs up, a

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:26.220
like, or a share, it

00:05:23.100 --> 00:05:28.620
really helps us with the algorithms on

00:05:26.220 --> 00:05:30.240
YouTube. They try to suppress some of my

00:05:28.620 --> 00:05:32.699
videos and I'm trying to get them out

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:36.120
there for the people. I really believe

00:05:32.699 --> 00:05:38.940
God put me on this platform to help

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:40.979
folks in these last days. There's a lot

00:05:38.940 --> 00:05:43.259
that I have inside of me to help people,

00:05:40.979 --> 00:05:45.780
and I want to get it out there. So

00:05:43.259 --> 00:05:47.880
if you could help us if you want to.

00:05:45.780 --> 00:05:51.320
All right, thank you so much for watching.

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:51.320
Have a blessed day. Bye.

